                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860719-70-defend788 t17860719-70-punish347"></join>
               To be confined twelve months in the House of Correction
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
